# NO MAGIC VALUES - EVER

## FORBIDDEN - Immediate Failure:

### Magic Numbers

```typescript
// ❌ FORBIDDEN
if (status === 404) {...}
setTimeout(() => {}, 3000)
padding: 16
width: 350

// ✅ REQUIRED
if (status === HTTP_STATUS.NOT_FOUND) {...}
setTimeout(() => {}, ANIMATION_DURATION.STANDARD)
padding: theme.spacing.md
width: CARD_WIDTH.DEFAULT
```

### Hardcoded Strings

```typescript
// ❌ FORBIDDEN
fetch('https://api.example.com/users')
if (role === 'admin') setError('Something went wrong')

// ✅ REQUIRED
fetch(`${process.env.NEXT_PUBLIC_API_URL}/users`)
if (role === USER_ROLES.ADMIN) setError(ERROR_MESSAGES.GENERIC)
```

### User-Facing Text (i18n)

**ALL user-facing text MUST use the dictionary pattern.** See `.cursor/rules/12-internationalization.mdc` for the full implementation guide.

```typescript
// ❌ FORBIDDEN
<h1>Merhaba Dünya</h1>
<Button>Kaydet</Button>

// ✅ REQUIRED
import { getDictionary } from '@/lib/dictionary'
const dict = await getDictionary()
...
<h1>{dict.page.home.title}</h1>
<Button>{dict.component.button.save}</Button>
```

### Inline Colors

```typescript
// ❌ FORBIDDEN
color: '#FF5733'
backgroundColor: 'rgb(255, 87, 51)'
borderColor: 'red'

// ✅ REQUIRED
color: theme.colors.primary
backgroundColor: 'bg-destructive'
borderColor: 'border-red-500'
```

## MANDATORY Constants Structure:

```typescript
// constants/index.ts
export const HTTP_STATUS = {
    OK: 200,
    NOT_FOUND: 404,
    SERVER_ERROR: 500,
} as const

export const ANIMATION_DURATION = {
    INSTANT: 0,
    FAST: 150,
    STANDARD: 300,
    SLOW: 500,
} as const

export const ERROR_MESSAGES = {
    GENERIC: 'An error occurred. Please try again.',
    NETWORK: 'Network error. Check your connection.',
    UNAUTHORIZED: 'You are not authorized to perform this action.',
} as const
```

## Environment Variables:

**ALL external URLs, API keys, and configuration MUST use env vars:**

```typescript
// ❌ FORBIDDEN
const API_URL = 'https://api.production.com'

// ✅ REQUIRED
const API_URL = process.env.NEXT_PUBLIC_API_URL
```

